  "status": "Current operational status of the hardware (IDLE, SLEWING, OBSERVING, ERROR).",
  "dome_open": "Whether the observatory dome is open and ready for observation.",
  "weather_condition": "Current atmospheric quality (e.g., CLEAR, CLOUDY, STORMY).",
